  "english": [
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>The priests</b> would <b>keep watch in three places in the Temple</b> courtyard, in honor of the Temple, like guards in royal courtyards: <b>In the Chamber of Avtinas,</b> which is the Chamber where the incense was prepared, <b>and</b> on the two sides of the northern section of the courtyard: <b>In the Chamber of the Spark,</b> where there was a small, perpetual fire, from which the fire of the altar would be lit if it went out; <b>and in the Chamber of the Hearth,</b> where there was also a fire, by which the priests would warm themselves when it was cold. <b>In the Chamber of Avtinas and in the Chamber of the Spark there were upper stories,</b> and <b>the young</b> priests, who were not yet eligible to serve in the Temple, would <b>keep watch there.</b>",
    "In <b>the Chamber of the Hearth,</b> there was no upper story, as its ceiling was round like <b>a cupola. And it was a large hall, surrounded</b> by <b>rows of stone</b> that protruded from the walls and that served as benches. <b>The elders of the patrilineal</b> priestly <b>family</b> that would serve in the Temple the following day would <b>sleep there, and the keys to the</b> Temple <b>courtyard</b> were <b>in their possession.</b>",
    "The <b>young men of the priesthood,</b> who were old enough to serve in the Temple, would also sleep in the Chamber of the Hearth. They would not sleep on benches, but instead <b>each</b> of the priests would sleep with <b>his garment on the ground.</b> Furthermore, <b>they would not sleep</b> dressed <b>in the sacred vestments; rather, they would remove</b> them and fold them up. <b>And</b> then <b>they</b> would <b>place</b> their vestments on the floor <b>beneath their heads, and cover themselves with their own</b> non-sacred <b>garments.</b> If <b>a seminal emission befell one of</b> the priests, rendering him ritually impure and unfit for service, <b>he would leave</b> the Chamber of the Hearth, <b>and he would walk</b>"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"0\" data-sentence-id=\"0\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"משנה\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>בִּשְׁלֹשָׁה</strong></big>",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>מְקוֹמוֹת הַכֹּהֲנִים",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "שׁוֹמְרִים בְּבֵית",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "הַמִּקְדָּשׁ: בֵּית",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "אַבְטִינָס, בֵּית",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "הַנִּיצוֹץ, בֵּית",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "הַמּוֹקֵד. בְּבֵית",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "אַבְטִינָס וּבְבֵית",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "הַנִּיצוֹץ הָיוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "עֲלִיּוֹת, הָרוֹבִים",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "שׁוֹמְרִים שָׁם.",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "בֵּית הַמּוֹקֵד",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "כִּיפָּה, וּבַיִת",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "הַגָּדוֹל הָיָה,",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "מוּקָּף רוֹבְדִין שֶׁל",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "אֶבֶן. זִקְנֵי בֵּית",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "אָב יְשֵׁנִים שָׁם",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "וּמַפְתְּחוֹת",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "הָעֲזָרָה בְּיָדָם.",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "פִּרְחֵי כְהוּנָּה",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "אִישׁ כִּסְתּוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "בָּאָרֶץ. לֹא הָיוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "יְשֵׁנִים בְּבִגְדֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "קֹדֶשׁ, אֶלָּא הָיוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "פּוֹשְׁטִין",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "וּמַנִּיחִין אוֹתָן",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "תַּחַת רָאשֵׁיהֶם,",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "וּמִתְכַּסִּין",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "בִּכְסוּת עַצְמָן.",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "אֵירַע קֶרִי לְאֶחָד",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "מֵהֶן – יוֹצֵא",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "280px",
      "width": "320px",
      "text": "וְהוֹלֵךְ לוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>בשלשה מקומות הכהנים שומרים בבית המקדש וכו'.</b> עד",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "סוף הפרקים פי' בשלשה מקומות הכהנים שומרים שימור",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "זה אינו משום חישוב גניבה דאין עניות במקום עשירות",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "אלא גזירת הכתוב הוא דכתיב ושמרו וגם כבוד המקדש",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "שלא יסיחו דעתם ממנו לא ביום ולא בלילה כדכתיב",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "ביהוידע [מ\"ב יא] ושמרתם את משמרת הבית מסח:",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>בית אבטינס.</b> לשכה שמפטמין בה את הקטורת. ואבטינס",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "היה ראש לאותו משפחה שהיו בקיאים בפטום הקטרת",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "כדאיתא ביומא [דף לח.] שלא רצו ללמד על מעשה",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "הקטורת:",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>בית הניצוץ.</b> כמין אכסדרה היתה פתוחה מרוח אחת",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "וניצוצי חמה מנצצין בה והיתה בה אורה מרובה לכך",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "נקראת הלשכה בית הניצוץ:",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>בית המוקד.</b> על שם שתמיד היה בה מדורות גדולות",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "להתחמם בהם הכהנים המהלכים יחפים על הרצפה",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "[ומלובשים] בכתונת א' נקראת בית המוקד:",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>היו עליות.</b> מפ' בגמ':",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 6",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>והרובים.</b> ילדים כדמתרגם ילד רביא שלא הגיעו לעבודה",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 6",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "והם זריזים לעלות בעליות [לפיכך] שומרים שם:",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 7",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>מוקף רובדין של אבן.</b> אצטבאות חתיכות של אבני גזית",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 7",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "בולטות מן החומה זו למעלה מזו ועליהם היו ישנים",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 7",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "זקני אותו בית אב שיש להם לעבוד למחר. ובית מוקד",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 7",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "היה חציו בנוי בקודש וחציו בחול:",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 8",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>ומפתחות העזרה בידם.</b> לשמור דלתות העזרה:",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 9",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>ופרחי כהונה.</b> אותן שהגיעו לכלל עבודה:",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 10",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "<b>איש כסותו בארץ.</b> כסת הוא הקטן שנותן אדם תחת",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 10",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "מראשותיו כשהוא ישן והגדול ששוכב כל גופו עליו הוא",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 10",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "נקרא כר. וכן מוכח במסכת כלים [פכ\"ח מ\"ה] דתנן",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 10",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "סדין שעשאו כר ומטפחת שעשאו כסת. וכן אמרינן בפרק",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 10",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "בתרא דעירובין [דף ק:] אשה נעשית כר לבעלה ואמרינן",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 10",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "נמי בפרק בתרא דע\"ז [דף סה וע\"ש בתוס' ד\"ה ה\"ג]",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    },
    {
      "source_ref": "Commentary of the Rosh on Tamid 25b: 10",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ],
      "text": "מניח אדם עליו כסתו ולגינו ול\"ג כסותו:",
      "left": "",
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "185px"
    }
  ],
  "vilna_piskaot": [],
  "steinsaltz_sugyot": [
